album.Chae Cubicle:
Nikon AF-S 85mm f/1.4G film photo. Soft and cozy ambient lighting.

(K-Pop idol Chaeyoung), dressed as the reference exposed her smooth fit midriff and wide hips, barefoot with delicated pattern black toe nails polish. She's sitting with legs crossed while she is smoking a thick well rolled joint of weed with her right hand and meanwhile with her left hand holding her smartphone with a black case cover that is plugged to the Headphones she is wearing to listen some music, she is on a netcafe private cubicle in Tokyo City. The cubicle have tatami comfy floor a tiny fridge and a shelf with chips and other candys, and of course, a Gaming PC in a comfy desktop at floor side. The monitor screen is behind of her showing "32.23 Studios". A poster witth the legend "PROMO 2x1 on Chips♥" can be seen behind of her up in the wall near other Japanese advertising showing promotions of the netcafe and some pictures advertising the other rooms and facilities the netcafe have to offer and a tiny sign with "Cubicle #44" to indicate the number of the cubicle easy to see for the client. In the desktop you can see a grinder with another well rolled joint for later and a beer can opened. --AR:16:9--
